# "PASTE_YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_HERE"

Go to the Google AI Studio, get your own free API key, and create your own local api_key.txt file.

Why?

Free-tier API keys have limits (like how many requests you can make per minute). 
If all four of us shared one key, 
We would hit that limit four times faster, causing the app to crash for everyone.

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_key
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_key
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:pass@host:5432/dbname